Package com.github.koshamo.fiddler

The main package contains all the classes needed for a standard fiddler based application

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    EventHandler
    A module that wants to register to the message bus to receive messages or notifications needs to implement this interface.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DataEvent<M,T>
    The DataEvent is the main Event for sending data all around a Fiddler application.
    Event
    The parent class of all Fiddler events.
    ExitEvent
    The exit event is a event, that is distributed to all modules registered to the message bus and calls their shutdown method.
    MessageBus
    The MessageBus class is the main class for a message based modularized application.
    MessageEvent
    The message event is a simple event, that can be used to distribute simple information along the Fiddler based application.
    RequestEvent<M>
    The RequestEvent is used to request a set of data.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    MessageBus.ListenerType
    The ListenerType is used to register EventHandlers to the MessageBus.
